{
  "video_id": "HbUeAdVXOVc",
  "title": "Erica Frenkel: The universal anesthesia machine",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16680.0,
      "end_time": 17529.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk to you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17554.0,
      "end_time": 21370.0,
      "text": "about the design of medical technology for low-resource settings."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21610.0,
      "end_time": 23414.0,
      "text": "I study health systems in these countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23438.0,
      "end_time": 25352.0,
      "text": "And one of the major gaps in care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25377.0,
      "end_time": 27350.0,
      "text": "almost across the board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27600.0,
      "end_time": 29226.0,
      "text": "is access to safe surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29251.0,
      "end_time": 31910.0,
      "text": "Now one of the major bottlenecks that we&#39;ve found"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31934.0,
      "end_time": 35169.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s sort of preventing both the access in the first place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35193.0,
      "end_time": 38629.0,
      "text": "and the safety of those surgeries that do happen, is anesthesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39106.0,
      "end_time": 41498.0,
      "text": "And actually, it&#39;s the model that we expect to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41522.0,
      "end_time": 44221.0,
      "text": "for delivering anesthesia in these environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44880.0,
      "end_time": 48733.0,
      "text": "Here, we have a scene that you would find in any operating room across the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48757.0,
      "end_time": 50233.0,
      "text": "or any other developed country."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50258.0,
      "end_time": 51445.0,
      "text": "In the background there"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51469.0,
      "end_time": 54400.0,
      "text": "is a very sophisticated anesthesia machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54640.0,
      "end_time": 57913.0,
      "text": "And this machine is able to enable surgery and save lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57937.0,
      "end_time": 61236.0,
      "text": "because it was designed with this environment in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61589.0,
      "end_time": 64521.0,
      "text": "In order to operate, this machine needs a number of things"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64545.0,
      "end_time": 66445.0,
      "text": "that this hospital has to offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66469.0,
      "end_time": 69836.0,
      "text": "It needs an extremely well-trained anesthesiologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69861.0,
      "end_time": 72312.0,
      "text": "with years of training with complex machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72336.0,
      "end_time": 74757.0,
      "text": "to help her monitor the flows of the gas"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74781.0,
      "end_time": 77344.0,
      "text": "and keep her patients safe and anesthetized"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77368.0,
      "end_time": 78818.0,
      "text": "throughout the surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78843.0,
      "end_time": 81610.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a delicate machine running on computer algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81634.0,
      "end_time": 84852.0,
      "text": "and it needs special care, TLC, to keep it up and running,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84876.0,
      "end_time": 86734.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to break pretty easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86758.0,
      "end_time": 89670.0,
      "text": "And when it does, it needs a team of biomedical engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89694.0,
      "end_time": 93300.0,
      "text": "who understand its complexities, can fix it, can source the parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93270.0,
      "end_time": 95259.0,
      "text": "and keep it saving lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95948.0,
      "end_time": 97482.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a pretty expensive machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97506.0,
      "end_time": 100147.0,
      "text": "It needs a hospital whose budget can allow it"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100171.0,
      "end_time": 105650.0,
      "text": "to support one machine costing upwards of 50 or $100,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105556.0,
      "end_time": 107455.0,
      "text": "And perhaps most obviously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107479.0,
      "end_time": 108993.0,
      "text": "but also most importantly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109170.0,
      "end_time": 111853.0,
      "text": "and the path to concepts that we&#39;ve heard about"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111877.0,
      "end_time": 113163.0,
      "text": "kind of illustrates this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113187.0,
      "end_time": 118333.0,
      "text": "it needs infrastructure that can supply an uninterrupted source of electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118357.0,
      "end_time": 121369.0,
      "text": "of compressed oxygen, and other medical supplies"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121393.0,
      "end_time": 125671.0,
      "text": "that are so critical to the functioning of this machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125695.0,
      "end_time": 128994.0,
      "text": "In other words, this machine requires a lot of stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129180.0,
      "end_time": 130991.0,
      "text": "that this hospital cannot offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131592.0,
      "end_time": 134612.0,
      "text": "This is the electrical supply for a hospital in rural Malawi."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135413.0,
      "end_time": 136574.0,
      "text": "In this hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136598.0,
      "end_time": 139269.0,
      "text": "there is one person qualified to deliver anesthesia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139293.0,
      "end_time": 140445.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s qualified"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140469.0,
      "end_time": 145450.0,
      "text": "because she has 12, maybe 18 months of training in anesthesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145690.0,
      "end_time": 147315.0,
      "text": "In the hospital and in the entire region"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147340.0,
      "end_time": 149347.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s not a single biomedical engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149371.0,
      "end_time": 150940.0,
      "text": "So when this machine breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150964.0,
      "end_time": 153173.0,
      "text": "the machines that they have to work with break,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153197.0,
      "end_time": 154966.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve got to try and figure it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154990.0,
      "end_time": 157282.0,
      "text": "but most of the time, that&#39;s the end of the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157306.0,
      "end_time": 159523.0,
      "text": "Those machines go the proverbial junkyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159547.0,
      "end_time": 161876.0,
      "text": "And the price tag of the machine that I mentioned"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161900.0,
      "end_time": 163961.0,
      "text": "could represent maybe a quarter or a third"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 163985.0,
      "end_time": 166797.0,
      "text": "of the annual operating budget for this hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167840.0,
      "end_time": 171224.0,
      "text": "And finally, I think you can see that infrastructure is not very strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171248.0,
      "end_time": 173922.0,
      "text": "This hospital is connected to a very weak power grid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173946.0,
      "end_time": 175728.0,
      "text": "one that goes down frequently."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175752.0,
      "end_time": 178298.0,
      "text": "So it runs frequently, the entire hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178322.0,
      "end_time": 179745.0,
      "text": "just on a generator."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 179769.0,
      "end_time": 181925.0,
      "text": "And you can imagine, the generator breaks down"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 181949.0,
      "end_time": 183261.0,
      "text": "or runs out of fuel."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 183621.0,
      "end_time": 185648.0,
      "text": "And the World Bank sees this"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 185672.0,
      "end_time": 189203.0,
      "text": "and estimates that a hospital in this setting in a low-income country"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189227.0,
      "end_time": 192303.0,
      "text": "can expect up to 18 power outages per month."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 193918.0,
      "end_time": 197111.0,
      "text": "Similarly, compressed oxygen and other medical supplies"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 197135.0,
      "end_time": 198316.0,
      "text": "are really a luxury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198341.0,
      "end_time": 201623.0,
      "text": "and can often be out of stock for months or even a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 201647.0,
      "end_time": 204810.0,
      "text": "So it seems crazy, but the model that we have right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 204835.0,
      "end_time": 207400.0,
      "text": "is taking those machines that were designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 209346.0,
      "text": "for that first environment that I showed you"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209371.0,
      "end_time": 213235.0,
      "text": "and donating or selling them to hospitals in this environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214121.0,
      "end_time": 215697.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just inappropriate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215721.0,
      "end_time": 218259.0,
      "text": "it becomes really unsafe."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 218776.0,
      "end_time": 220698.0,
      "text": "One of our partners at Johns Hopkins"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220722.0,
      "end_time": 224901.0,
      "text": "was observing surgeries in Sierra Leone about a year ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225485.0,
      "end_time": 228818.0,
      "text": "And the first surgery of the day happened to be an obstetrical case."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 228842.0,
      "end_time": 231825.0,
      "text": "A woman came in, she needed an emergency C-section"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231849.0,
      "end_time": 234578.0,
      "text": "to save her life and the life of her baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235650.0,
      "end_time": 237190.0,
      "text": "And everything began pretty auspiciously."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 237430.0,
      "end_time": 239296.0,
      "text": "The surgeon was on call and scrubbed in."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239320.0,
      "end_time": 240608.0,
      "text": "The nurse was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240632.0,
      "end_time": 243493.0,
      "text": "She was able to anesthetize her quickly, and it was important"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 243517.0,
      "end_time": 245853.0,
      "text": "because of the emergency nature of the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 245877.0,
      "end_time": 247594.0,
      "text": "And everything began well"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 247618.0,
      "end_time": 249690.0,
      "text": "until the power went out."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 251330.0,
      "end_time": 252857.0,
      "text": "And now in the middle of this surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252881.0,
      "end_time": 255950.0,
      "text": "the surgeon is racing against the clock to finish his case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255974.0,
      "end_time": 258325.0,
      "text": "which he can do -- he&#39;s got a headlamp."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 258350.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262411.0,
      "text": "But the nurse is literally running around a darkened operating theater"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 262435.0,
      "end_time": 265390.0,
      "text": "trying to find anything she can use to anesthetize her patient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 265414.0,
      "end_time": 267103.0,
      "text": "to keep her patient asleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 267127.0,
      "end_time": 270100.0,
      "text": "Because her machine doesn&#39;t work when there&#39;s no power."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 270697.0,
      "end_time": 273751.0,
      "text": "This routine surgery that many of you have probably experienced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 273775.0,
      "end_time": 278248.0,
      "text": "and others are probably the product of, has now become a tragedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 278915.0,
      "end_time": 281651.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s so frustrating is this is not a singular event;"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 281675.0,
      "end_time": 284174.0,
      "text": "this happens across the developing world."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284198.0,
      "end_time": 287150.0,
      "text": "35 million surgeries are attempted every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 287175.0,
      "end_time": 288771.0,
      "text": "without safe anesthesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 289470.0,
      "end_time": 292382.0,
      "text": "My colleague, Dr. Paul Fenton, was living this reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 292406.0,
      "end_time": 294236.0,
      "text": "He was the chief of anesthesiology"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296760.0,
      "text": "in a hospital in Malawi, a teaching hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 297288.0,
      "end_time": 298782.0,
      "text": "He went to work every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 298806.0,
      "end_time": 300774.0,
      "text": "in an operating theater like this one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 300798.0,
      "end_time": 303937.0,
      "text": "trying to deliver anesthesia and teach others how to do so"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 303961.0,
      "end_time": 305236.0,
      "text": "using that same equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 309570.0,
      "text": "that became so unreliable, and frankly unsafe, in his hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 310299.0,
      "end_time": 312780.0,
      "text": "And after umpteen surgeries"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 312103.0,
      "end_time": 314671.0,
      "text": "and, you can imagine, really unspeakable tragedy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 314695.0,
      "end_time": 317370.0,
      "text": "he just said, \"That&#39;s it. I&#39;m done. That&#39;s enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 317610.0,
      "end_time": 319131.0,
      "text": "There has to be something better.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 319489.0,
      "end_time": 321360.0,
      "text": "He took a walk down the hall"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 321600.0,
      "end_time": 324491.0,
      "text": "to where they threw all those machines that had just crapped out on them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 324515.0,
      "end_time": 326192.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s the scientific term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 326216.0,
      "end_time": 327558.0,
      "text": "and he started tinkering."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 327582.0,
      "end_time": 329935.0,
      "text": "He took one part from here and another from there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 329959.0,
      "end_time": 332541.0,
      "text": "and he tried to come up with a machine that would work"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 332565.0,
      "end_time": 334193.0,
      "text": "in the reality that he was facing."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 334217.0,
      "end_time": 335431.0,
      "text": "And what he came up with:"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335455.0,
      "end_time": 336777.0,
      "text": "was this guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 336802.0,
      "end_time": 340339.0,
      "text": "The prototype for the Universal Anesthesia Machine --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 340363.0,
      "end_time": 343660.0,
      "text": "a machine that would work and anesthetize his patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 343684.0,
      "end_time": 347259.0,
      "text": "no matter the circumstances that his hospital had to offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 347779.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "Here it is, back at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 349284.0,
      "end_time": 352712.0,
      "text": "at that same hospital, developed a little further, 12 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 352737.0,
      "end_time": 355917.0,
      "text": "working on patients from pediatrics to geriatrics."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 356397.0,
      "end_time": 359167.0,
      "text": "Let me show you a little bit about how this machine works."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 359191.0,
      "end_time": 361680.0,
      "text": "Voila!"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 361712.0,
      "end_time": 362919.0,
      "text": "Here she is."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 362943.0,
      "end_time": 364187.0,
      "text": "When you have electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 364211.0,
      "end_time": 367229.0,
      "text": "everything in this machine begins in the base."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 367253.0,
      "end_time": 369849.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a built-in oxygen concentrator down there."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369874.0,
      "end_time": 373300.0,
      "text": "Now you&#39;ve heard me mention oxygen a few times at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 373270.0,
      "end_time": 376815.0,
      "text": "Essentially, to deliver anesthesia, you want as pure oxygen as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 376839.0,
      "end_time": 380262.0,
      "text": "because eventually you&#39;re going to dilute it, essentially, with the gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 380286.0,
      "end_time": 382722.0,
      "text": "And the mixture that the patient inhales"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 382746.0,
      "end_time": 385560.0,
      "text": "needs to be at least a certain percentage oxygen"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 385810.0,
      "end_time": 386767.0,
      "text": "or else it can become dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 386791.0,
      "end_time": 388709.0,
      "text": "But so in here when there&#39;s electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 388733.0,
      "end_time": 391608.0,
      "text": "the oxygen concentrator takes in room air."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 391632.0,
      "end_time": 394911.0,
      "text": "Now we know room air is gloriously free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 394935.0,
      "end_time": 396236.0,
      "text": "it is abundant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398259.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s already 21 percent oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 398696.0,
      "end_time": 402373.0,
      "text": "So all this concentrator does is take that room air in, filter it"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 402397.0,
      "end_time": 406217.0,
      "text": "and send 95 percent pure oxygen up and across here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 406241.0,
      "end_time": 408447.0,
      "text": "where it mixes with the anesthetic agent."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 409300.0,
      "end_time": 412627.0,
      "text": "Now before that mixture hits the patient&#39;s lungs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 412651.0,
      "end_time": 414865.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going to pass by here -- you can&#39;t see it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 414889.0,
      "end_time": 416671.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s an oxygen sensor here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 416695.0,
      "end_time": 420900.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s going to read out on this screen the percentage of oxygen being delivered."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 421544.0,
      "end_time": 423518.0,
      "text": "Now if you don&#39;t have power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 423542.0,
      "end_time": 427147.0,
      "text": "or, God forbid, the power cuts out in the middle of a surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 427172.0,
      "end_time": 429516.0,
      "text": "this machine transitions automatically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 429540.0,
      "end_time": 431289.0,
      "text": "without even having to touch it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 431313.0,
      "end_time": 433644.0,
      "text": "to drawing in room air from this inlet."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 434650.0,
      "end_time": 435401.0,
      "text": "Everything else is the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 435425.0,
      "end_time": 437210.0,
      "text": "The only difference is that now"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 437450.0,
      "end_time": 440259.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re only working with 21 percent oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 440666.0,
      "end_time": 443487.0,
      "text": "Now that used to be a dangerous guessing game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 443511.0,
      "end_time": 445897.0,
      "text": "because you only knew if you gave too little oxygen"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 445921.0,
      "end_time": 447296.0,
      "text": "once something bad happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 447321.0,
      "end_time": 450340.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve put a long-life battery backup on here."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 450580.0,
      "end_time": 452252.0,
      "text": "This is the only part that&#39;s battery backed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 452276.0,
      "end_time": 455681.0,
      "text": "But this gives control to the provider, whether there&#39;s power or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 455705.0,
      "end_time": 457298.0,
      "text": "because they can adjust the flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 457322.0,
      "end_time": 461290.0,
      "text": "based on the percentage of oxygen they see that they&#39;re giving the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 461314.0,
      "end_time": 464659.0,
      "text": "In both cases, whether you have power or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 464683.0,
      "end_time": 466723.0,
      "text": "sometimes the patient needs help breathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 466747.0,
      "end_time": 469948.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a reality of anesthesia, the lungs can be paralyzed."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 469972.0,
      "end_time": 472560.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;ve just added this manual bellows."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 472800.0,
      "end_time": 475700.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen surgeries for three or four hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 475950.0,
      "end_time": 476953.0,
      "text": "to ventilate the patient on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 477684.0,
      "end_time": 480672.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a straightforward machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 480696.0,
      "end_time": 483601.0,
      "text": "I shudder to say simple; it&#39;s straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 484196.0,
      "end_time": 486970.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s by design."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 486121.0,
      "end_time": 491320.0,
      "text": "You do not need to be a highly trained, specialized anesthesiologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 491345.0,
      "end_time": 492516.0,
      "text": "to use this machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 492540.0,
      "end_time": 495292.0,
      "text": "which is good because, in these rural district hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 495316.0,
      "end_time": 497911.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not going to get that level of training."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 497935.0,
      "end_time": 501630.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also designed for the environment that it will be used in."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 501870.0,
      "end_time": 502864.0,
      "text": "This is an incredibly rugged machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 502888.0,
      "end_time": 506342.0,
      "text": "It has to stand up to the heat and the wear and tear"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 506367.0,
      "end_time": 509485.0,
      "text": "that happens in hospitals in these rural districts."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 509509.0,
      "end_time": 511904.0,
      "text": "And so it&#39;s not going to break very easily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 511928.0,
      "end_time": 515202.0,
      "text": "but if it does, virtually every piece in this machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 515226.0,
      "end_time": 517236.0,
      "text": "can be swapped out and replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519254.0,
      "text": "with a hex wrench and a screwdriver."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 521100.0,
      "end_time": 523270.0,
      "text": "And finally, it&#39;s affordable."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 523294.0,
      "end_time": 526947.0,
      "text": "This machine comes in at an eighth of the cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 526971.0,
      "end_time": 530490.0,
      "text": "of the conventional machine that I showed you earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 530730.0,
      "end_time": 534561.0,
      "text": "So in other words, what we have here is a machine that can enable surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 534585.0,
      "end_time": 535757.0,
      "text": "and save lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 535781.0,
      "end_time": 538771.0,
      "text": "because it was designed for its environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 538795.0,
      "end_time": 541213.0,
      "text": "just like the first machine I showed you."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 541237.0,
      "end_time": 543241.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re not content to stop there."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 543265.0,
      "end_time": 544439.0,
      "text": "Is it working?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 544464.0,
      "end_time": 547460.0,
      "text": "Is this the design that&#39;s going to work in place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 547700.0,
      "end_time": 548837.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;ve seen good results so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 548861.0,
      "end_time": 552246.0,
      "text": "This is in 13 hospitals in four countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 552270.0,
      "end_time": 556203.0,
      "text": "and since 2010, we&#39;ve done well over 2,000 surgeries"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 556227.0,
      "end_time": 558459.0,
      "text": "with no clinically adverse events."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 558800.0,
      "end_time": 559967.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re thrilled."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 559991.0,
      "end_time": 564413.0,
      "text": "This really seems like a cost-effective, scalable solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 564437.0,
      "end_time": 566470.0,
      "text": "to a problem that&#39;s really pervasive."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 566958.0,
      "end_time": 568558.0,
      "text": "But we still want to be sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 568582.0,
      "end_time": 570999.0,
      "text": "that this is the most effective and safe device"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 571230.0,
      "end_time": 573800.0,
      "text": "that we can be putting into hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 573104.0,
      "end_time": 575628.0,
      "text": "So to do that, we&#39;ve launched a number of partnerships"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 575652.0,
      "end_time": 577138.0,
      "text": "with NGOs and universities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 577162.0,
      "end_time": 579811.0,
      "text": "to gather data on the user interface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 579835.0,
      "end_time": 582270.0,
      "text": "on the types of surgeries it&#39;s appropriate for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 582510.0,
      "end_time": 584438.0,
      "text": "and ways we can enhance the device itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 584462.0,
      "end_time": 587116.0,
      "text": "One of those partnerships is with Johns Hopkins"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 587140.0,
      "end_time": 588513.0,
      "text": "just here in Baltimore."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 588537.0,
      "end_time": 592815.0,
      "text": "They have a really cool anesthesia simulation lab out in Baltimore."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 592839.0,
      "end_time": 594720.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re taking this machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 594744.0,
      "end_time": 598318.0,
      "text": "and recreating some of the operating theater crises"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 598342.0,
      "end_time": 599848.0,
      "text": "that this machine might face"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 599873.0,
      "end_time": 602236.0,
      "text": "in one of the hospitals that it&#39;s intended for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604384.0,
      "text": "and in a contained, safe environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 604408.0,
      "end_time": 606125.0,
      "text": "evaluating its effectiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 606607.0,
      "end_time": 610238.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re then able to compare the results from that study"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 610263.0,
      "end_time": 611683.0,
      "text": "with real-world experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 611707.0,
      "end_time": 613904.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re putting two of these in hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 613928.0,
      "end_time": 616790.0,
      "text": "that Johns Hopkins works with in Sierra Leone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 616103.0,
      "end_time": 619217.0,
      "text": "including the hospital where that emergency C-section happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 620645.0,
      "end_time": 623773.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve talked a lot about anesthesia, and I tend to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 623797.0,
      "end_time": 627889.0,
      "text": "I think it is incredibly fascinating and an important component of health."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 627913.0,
      "end_time": 630544.0,
      "text": "And it really seems peripheral, we never think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 630568.0,
      "end_time": 632771.0,
      "text": "until we don&#39;t have access to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 632796.0,
      "end_time": 634758.0,
      "text": "and then it becomes a gatekeeper."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 634782.0,
      "end_time": 636751.0,
      "text": "Who gets surgery and who doesn&#39;t?"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 637840.0,
      "end_time": 639814.0,
      "text": "Who gets safe surgery and who doesn&#39;t?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 640476.0,
      "end_time": 642939.0,
      "text": "But you know, it&#39;s just one of so many ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 642963.0,
      "end_time": 646690.0,
      "text": "that design, appropriate design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 646940.0,
      "end_time": 648700.0,
      "text": "can have an impact on health outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 648578.0,
      "end_time": 650697.0,
      "text": "If more people in the health-delivery space"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 650721.0,
      "end_time": 654290.0,
      "text": "really working on some of these challenges in low-income countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 654314.0,
      "end_time": 657967.0,
      "text": "could start their design process, their solution search,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 657991.0,
      "end_time": 659929.0,
      "text": "from outside of that proverbial box"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 659953.0,
      "end_time": 661891.0,
      "text": "and inside of the hospital --"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 661915.0,
      "end_time": 663746.0,
      "text": "In other words, if we could design"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 663770.0,
      "end_time": 666961.0,
      "text": "for the environment that exists in so many parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 666985.0,
      "end_time": 669394.0,
      "text": "rather than the one that we wished existed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 669418.0,
      "end_time": 671584.0,
      "text": "we might just save a lot of lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 672470.0,
      "end_time": 673515.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 673539.0,
      "end_time": 677973.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}